creator: H. A. Guerber
description:
LibriVox recording of The Story of the Romans by H. A. Guerber.
Read in English by twalter8; Felipe Vogel; J Korth; Kelvin D; Kevin Nieman; winonawyatt; Jane Kuplevatsky; jkbuchanan; Kangaroo692; Joel Wodhams; Sarah H.; Jarvious; Grace Durrant; CliffClaven; Ken Masters; Firetech; HariRK; Joseph Schnebelen; johnnyenglish; Ryan Cherrick; levispann; Soumen Barua; carteki; marbenx; Leah Chamblee; Wilburness; sarah louise pieplow; AnnaMarie Tokas; JamesPVMiller; Peter O'Malley; Larry Greene; Hultstrand; Jamie; Sebastien Blouin; Ashley
A collection of short stories and histories of Rome, from its beginning to its end. (Ann Boulais)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
